125
00:08:30,718 --> 00:08:32,720
YAMAI AND THE GANG

126
00:08:32,803 --> 00:08:34,388
<i>Something's in the water.</i>

127
00:08:35,515 --> 00:08:38,726
Let's see who can
hold their breath longest!

128
00:08:39,477 --> 00:08:42,438
The first one up buys the winner a soda.

129
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:45,191
