131
00:09:11,842 --> 00:09:14,971
Hey, Komi, um…

132
00:09:30,069 --> 00:09:32,530
Oh, it's nothing.

133
00:09:33,948 --> 00:09:35,324
Whew.

134
00:09:36,284 --> 00:09:37,535
This sure is fun.

135
00:09:42,206 --> 00:09:43,249
Wow!

136
00:09:43,332 --> 00:09:45,459
Alright! To the diving board next!

137
00:09:45,543 --> 00:09:46,794
Running is dangerou…

138
00:09:47,378 --> 00:09:48,212
Komi!

139
