143
00:10:06,522 --> 00:10:08,608
Komi, are you alright?

144
00:10:08,691 --> 00:10:10,359
NOD…

145
00:10:11,110 --> 00:10:13,946
<i>Wow, talk about bad vibes.</i>

146
00:10:14,030 --> 00:10:17,408
