148
00:10:20,328 --> 00:10:21,662
Y-Yes!

149
00:10:21,746 --> 00:10:22,913
I agree.

150
00:10:22,997 --> 00:10:24,123
SHAKE SHAKE

151
00:10:26,125 --> 00:10:29,920
-FRET
-NOTHING TO WRITE WITH!

152
00:10:30,004 --> 00:10:31,255
I'll bring it.

153
00:10:31,339 --> 00:10:33,716
DON'T WORRY ABOUT ME. GO HAVE FUN.

154
00:10:33,799 --> 00:10:35,760
B-But…

155
00:10:35,843 --> 00:10:36,677
Alright!

156
00:10:36,761 --> 00:10:39,680
Okay, let's all go
to the lazy river again!

157
00:10:39,764 --> 00:10:41,724
Hey, hang on.

158
00:10:42,224 --> 00:10:44,268
-Let's go, everyone!
-Hey, wait.

159
00:10:44,352 --> 00:10:45,478
You too, Yamai!

160
00:10:45,561 --> 00:10:47,521
Um, no, I'm…

161
00:10:47,605 --> 00:10:51,025
Komi, you stay with our bags and rest!

162
00:10:51,609 --> 00:10:52,526
NOD

163
00:10:58,574 --> 00:11:01,369
Najimi, hang on. I…

164
00:11:01,452 --> 00:11:05,039
Times like this, it's best to
have fun and not fuss.

165
00:11:06,207 --> 00:11:09,919
Otherwise she'll think it's her fault
for ruining our good time.

166
00:11:10,002 --> 00:11:11,420
Komi will feel bad, right?

167
00:11:11,504 --> 00:11:14,590
You've learned how to read the room.

168
00:11:14,673 --> 00:11:17,426
Huh? You mean I haven't
always been reading it?

169
00:11:17,510 --> 00:11:19,845
That's not the issue.

170
00:11:19,929 --> 00:11:22,640
I'm going to file down that bad poolside.

171
00:11:22,723 --> 00:11:25,184
I wanted to say that's why I'm not going.

172
00:11:32,858 --> 00:11:34,110
Where to next?

173
00:11:47,832 --> 00:11:49,667
Does it still hurt?

174
00:11:50,459 --> 00:11:53,421
Oh, sorry I startled you.

175
00:11:53,504 --> 00:11:55,256
DIDN'T YOU GO TO THE LAZY RIVER?

176
00:11:55,339 --> 00:11:58,384
Oh, I'm tired so I decided
to take a break.

177
00:12:11,647 --> 00:12:13,149
It's alright.

178
00:12:14,692 --> 00:12:16,861
Najimi and Agari are having fun.

179
00:12:17,945 --> 00:12:21,740
Yamai and the gang are filing down
the spot where you tripped.

180
00:12:22,992 --> 00:12:25,953
Yeah, I don't really get it either,

181
00:12:26,620 --> 00:12:29,665
but your friends
are all good people, Komi.

182
00:12:30,708 --> 00:12:33,711
You don't have to worry
that they'll hate you.

183
00:12:47,433 --> 00:12:50,352
I HAD FUN.

184
00:12:55,441 --> 00:12:58,486
IT WAS SO FUN BEING IN THE POOL
WITH EVERYONE.

185
00:12:58,569 --> 00:13:03,365
BUT I RUINED EVERYONE'S GOOD TIME…

186
00:13:03,449 --> 00:13:05,868
I HATE THIS FEELING.

187
00:13:19,507 --> 00:13:20,758
Komi!

188
00:13:28,516 --> 00:13:32,269
If you look sad,
nobody will be able to have a good time.

189
00:13:38,275 --> 00:13:39,276
Can you stand?

190
00:13:54,667 --> 00:13:58,170
-Komi's hand! Oh, never mind!
-NOTICED HE WAS HOLDING HER HAND.

191
00:14:08,681 --> 00:14:10,558
