192
00:14:10,641 --> 00:14:11,642
Hey, hey!

193
00:14:11,725 --> 00:14:14,353
Enough with the teenage drama!

194
00:14:15,729 --> 00:14:18,190
We bought these so you can play too, Komi.

195
00:14:18,274 --> 00:14:21,902
